=== TECHNOLOGY STACK AND DEPENDENCIES ===

This project relies on established open-source and local AI tooling:

- MarkItDown
  - Origin: Microsoft repository for OCR and file conversion to Markdown.
  - Usage in Proyecto_Kofu: Process multiple input formats including PDF, DOCX,
    PPTX, images, and audio.
  - Included in the project as an editable folder: `markitdown/`
  - Link: https://github.com/microsoft/markitdown

- Ollama with Gemma 4
  - Usage: Offline reasoning, code sanitization, and local processing.
  - Current Proyecto_Kofu version (0.7 Beta) uses this local LLM for reasoning
    and sanitization.
  - Link: https://ollama.ai/

All third-party dependencies are subject to their own license terms and must be
respected in addition to this license. This includes the license terms for
Ollama and MarkItDown.

