=== VERSION ROADMAP AND FUTURE PLANS ===

- v0.7 Beta
  - Current development version.
  - Uses Ollama with Gemma 4 for reasoning and sanitization.
  - The AI is not autonomous in beta and may fail due to address resolution errors.
  - Includes MarkItDown for OCR and file conversion.
  - Available for personal use, educational use with attribution, and restricted
    commercial use.

- v1.0 Stable
  - First stable version of the project.
  - Autonomous behavior is intended in this release.
  - Continuous maintenance and support.
  - Educational use permitted with logos and attribution.
  - Commercial use only with minimal modifications for functionality.

- v1.2 Stable and Optimized
  - Long-term stable version with performance optimizations.
  - Focused on speed and efficiency.
  - Commercial use limited under license.
  - Special educational versions are available with school-focused controls.

Version Use Policy:
- Personal use may use versions later than 1.2.
- Educational use may use versions earlier than 1.2 or special educational versions
  based on 1.2+.
- Normal versions beyond 1.2 are not permitted for general educational contexts.
- Commercial use may use versions earlier than 1.2 with at least 80% code
  modification, or version 1.0 with minimal code changes for functionality.
- The program may not be used as-is for commercial use.

